{"tid":1029334,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"閂門撚 - 閂車門用力定溫柔？","createTime":"2019-02-20T07:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T02:57:39.000Z","uid":48304,"like":45,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"dce55e18252c6f63802ee33d0ac91524c8b650b1","tid":1029334,"uid":48304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"老一輩通常都係偏大力咁閂車，逢逢聲，驚閂唔實（唔係惡意嘭門咁極端）<br />\n但後生通常都好撚輕手，大力少少都驚整親部車<br />\n<br />\n你地係邊種？<br />\n<br />\n利申：用力撚 由幾歲開始搭老豆車屋企教都係咁閂 真係咁易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n用力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溫柔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e0cc5b41e2633f91a79f4d198bbf70d9496336","tid":1029334,"uid":235683,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"講真壞就唔會咁易壞，但如果你坐車入面，人地咁大力山你道門，成架車會係震一震，如果你渣架係日本車，好似會就散咁<br />\n<br />\n感覺唔好"},{"pid":"11cad2fbcc7ff3244f5c3d579a729b2be073f52d","tid":1029334,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:23:22.000Z","msg":"中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05200822b68c1203c58d44b0911ffdaa4d321e49","tid":1029334,"uid":50935,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:24:09.000Z","msg":"陰力"},{"pid":"79bc3d4f20475448f86a91a792832aae12d68cbf","tid":1029334,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"用溫柔既大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553baa6e63adb37ed1d98cbc881a634153c0c71b","tid":1029334,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:26:59.000Z","msg":"唔閂"},{"pid":"4b260cc652315ed03066f97b465c938e2e5ca28d","tid":1029334,"uid":23897,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"捉實個手柄閂<br />\n度力啱啱好"},{"pid":"bd99db7a03a4603e5d5a2eb420b7